<view class="page"><view class="title">系统设置</view><view class="subtitle">配置小程序业务服务和查看外部集成状态</view><view class="card section"><label wx:if="{{isDevEnv}}" class="field"><view class="field-label">业务 API 地址（仅开发/体验版可改）</view><input class="input" value="{{apiBase}}" bindinput="input" placeholder="https://your-domain.com/api" /></label><view wx:else class="field"><view class="field-label">业务 API 地址</view><view class="picker" style="color:#8a93a8">{{apiBase}}</view></view><view class="toolbar"><button class="secondary" bindtap="health">测试连接</button><button wx:if="{{isDevEnv}}" class="primary" loading="{{saving}}" bindtap="save">保存设置</button></view><view class="small" style="margin-top:20rpx">正式版固定使用已配置小程序服务器域名，不支持切换，避免登录态被诱导发往第三方服务器。</view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">外部服务</view><view class="divider"></view><view class="row between"><text>当前模式</text><text class="tag">{{providers.mode||'未知'}}</text></view><view class="row between" style="margin-top:22rpx"><text>保司 API</text><text class="tag {{providers.insurer_api?'tag-success':'tag-gray'}}">{{providers.insurer_api?'已配置':'未配置'}}</text></view><view class="row between" style="margin-top:22rpx"><text>短信服务</text><text class="tag {{providers.sms?'tag-success':'tag-gray'}}">{{providers.sms?'已配置':'未配置'}}</text></view><view class="row between" style="margin-top:22rpx"><text>邮件服务</text><text class="tag {{providers.email?'tag-success':'tag-gray'}}">{{providers.email?'已配置':'未配置'}}</text></view><view class="row between" style="margin-top:22rpx"><text>支付服务</text><text class="tag {{providers.payment?'tag-success':'tag-gray'}}">{{providers.payment?'已配置':'未配置'}}</text></view></view></view>
